c%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170829173040&h=a400d395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三個女仔都咁靚～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170829/photo/bkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170829173040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170829173040&h=fc1e7abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錫錫～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170829/photo/bkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170829173040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170829173040&h=7d3b1f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瞓吓先！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170829/photo/bkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170829173040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170829173040&h=9e2e1453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食好西～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170829/photo/bkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_09b.jpg?20170829173040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20170829173040&h=1f0b7174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余思霆同Tyrese之前被東網拍到佢哋去拍拖。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n尋日係七夕情人節，圈中愛侶都趁機放閃晒恩愛，但應屆華姐冠軍余思霆冇陪男友Tyrese過節，反而同陌生人度過七夕，咁奇怪？<br />\n<br />\n原來余思霆最近返美國紐約探親友，咁啱回程嘅時間撞正係七夕，於是喺飛機上過節。不過佢就喺社交網上載多張靚相，當中仲有性感泳裝照，相當火辣！相中余思霆着上三點式玩水，大晒噴血事業線，豐滿上圍表露無遺，其中一張相仲見到有位小鮮肉喺佢隔籬添，而佢仲甫全身相騷長腿，獲網民大讚身材勁好！<br />\n<br />\n余思霆留言話：「下飛機才發現，原來我的情人節在飛機上過了！祝大家七夕快樂！已經開始想念家人，朋友這次離開紐約特別的不捨，因為下一次回去不知道是什（甚）麼時候了～ New York!! I'll miss you! 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170829/bkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170829%2Fbkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001.html&d=8z1brvdlsQg%2B6kaZjdJoAghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9c2df4e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170829/bkn-20170829171051928-0829_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b528b6c6a2bfc26b265edbc4c39ebeb6fd7a492b","tid":380084,"uid":136645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"髮線拍得住坤哥"}]}